{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
    "name": "Simple Voting API",
    "description": "Collection para o módulo simple_voting (Drupal 10). Todos os endpoints exigem autenticação via Basic Auth.\n\nO endpoint POST /votes adicionalmente exige o header X-CSRF-Token, obtido fazendo um GET autenticado em {{base_url}}/session/token.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "https://simplevoting.lndo.site",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "URL base da instalação Drupal. Altere para o ambiente desejado (local, staging, prod)."
    },
    {
      "key": "username",
      "value": "admin",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Usuário para Basic Auth."
    },
    {
      "key": "password",
      "value": "admin",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Senha para Basic Auth."
    },
    {
      "key": "question_id",
      "value": "enquete-exemplo",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Machine name da enquete usada nos endpoints que recebem {id}."
    },
    {
      "key": "csrf_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Token obtido via GET {{base_url}}/session/token. Necessário apenas no POST /votes quando autenticado por sessão (cookie)."
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "basic",
    "basic": [
      {
        "key": "username",
        "value": "{{username}}",
        "type": "string"
      },
      {
        "key": "password",
        "value": "{{password}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "GET questions — lista enquetes abertas",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/voting/v1/questions",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "voting", "v1", "questions"]
        },
        "description": "Retorna todas as enquetes com status aberto.\n\nResposta 200:\n```json\n{\n  \"data\": [\n    { \"id\": \"enquete-exemplo\", \"title\": \"Qual sua linguagem favorita?\", \"show_results\": true }\n  ]\n}\n```"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "200 OK — lista de enquetes",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "header": [
            { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
          ],
          "body": "{\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"enquete-exemplo\",\n      \"title\": \"Qual sua linguagem favorita?\",\n      \"show_results\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}",
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json"
        },
        {
          "name": "401 Unauthorized — sem credenciais",
          "status": "Unauthorized",
          "code": 401,
          "header": [
            { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
          ],
          "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Access denied\"\n}",
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "GET question/:id — detalhes e opções",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/voting/v1/questions/{{question_id}}",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "voting", "v1", "questions", "{{question_id}}"]
        },
        "description": "Retorna os dados da enquete e a lista de opções disponíveis para votação.\n\nResposta 200:\n```json\n{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": \"enquete-exemplo\",\n    \"title\": \"Qual sua linguagem favorita?\",\n    \"status\": \"open\",\n    \"show_results\": true,\n    \"options\": [\n      { \"id\": 1, \"title\": \"PHP\" },\n      { \"id\": 2, \"title\": \"Python\" }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "200 OK — enquete com opções",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "header": [
            { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
          ],
          "body": "{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": \"enquete-exemplo\",\n    \"title\": \"Qual sua linguagem favorita?\",\n    \"status\": \"open\",\n    \"show_results\": true,\n    \"options\": [\n      { \"id\": 1, \"title\": \"PHP\" },\n      { \"id\": 2, \"title\": \"Python\" },\n      { \"id\": 3, \"title\": \"JavaScript\" }\n    ]\n  }\n}",
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json"
        },
        {
          "name": "404 Not Found — enquete inexistente",
          "status": "Not Found",
          "code": 404,
          "header": [
            { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
          ],
          "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Not Found\"\n}",
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "POST vote — registra um voto",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          },
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json"
          },
          {
            "key": "X-CSRF-Token",
            "value": "{{csrf_token}}",
            "description": "Obrigatório quando autenticado por sessão (cookie). Clientes Basic Auth podem omitir, pois são stateless.",
            "disabled": false
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"question_id\": \"{{question_id}}\",\n  \"option_id\": 1\n}",
          "options": {
            "raw": {
              "language": "json"
            }
          }
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/voting/v1/votes",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "voting", "v1", "votes"]
        },
        "description": "Registra o voto do usuário autenticado. Cada usuário pode votar uma única vez por enquete — uma segunda tentativa retorna 409 Conflict.\n\nBody obrigatório:\n```json\n{\n  \"question_id\": \"enquete-exemplo\",\n  \"option_id\": 1\n}\n```\n\nPara obter o X-CSRF-Token faça:\n```\nGET {{base_url}}/session/token\n```\n(necessário apenas em clientes com sessão, ex.: chamadas via browser/cookie)"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "201 Created — voto registrado",
          "status": "Created",
          "code": 201,
          "header": [
            { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
          ],
          "body": "{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"message\": \"Voto registrado com sucesso.\"\n  }\n}",
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json"
        },
        {
          "name": "400 Bad Request — campos ausentes",
          "status": "Bad Request",
          "code": 400,
          "header": [
            { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
          ],
          "body": "{\n  \"error\": \"Os campos question_id e option_id são obrigatórios.\"\n}",
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json"
        },
        {
          "name": "401 Unauthorized — não autenticado",
          "status": "Unauthorized",
          "code": 401,
          "header": [
            { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
            { "key": "WWW-Authenticate", "value": "Basic realm=\"Simple Voting API\"" }
          ],
          "body": "{\n  \"error\": \"Autenticação necessária para registrar um voto.\"\n}",
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json"
        },
        {
          "name": "409 Conflict — voto duplicado",
          "status": "Conflict",
          "code": 409,
          "header": [
            { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
          ],
          "body": "{\n  \"error\": \"Você já votou nessa enquete.\"\n}",
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "GET results/:id — resultados da enquete",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/voting/v1/questions/{{question_id}}/results",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "voting", "v1", "questions", "{{question_id}}", "results"]
        },
        "description": "Retorna o total de votos por opção. Disponível apenas quando a enquete tem `show_results: true`; caso contrário retorna 403.\n\nResposta 200:\n```json\n{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"question_id\": \"enquete-exemplo\",\n    \"title\": \"Qual sua linguagem favorita?\",\n    \"total_votes\": 42,\n    \"options\": [\n      { \"id\": 1, \"title\": \"PHP\", \"votes\": 20, \"percentage\": 47.6 },\n      { \"id\": 2, \"title\": \"Python\", \"votes\": 15, \"percentage\": 35.7 },\n      { \"id\": 3, \"title\": \"JavaScript\", \"votes\": 7, \"percentage\": 16.7 }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "200 OK — resultados",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "header": [
            { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
          ],
          "body": "{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"question_id\": \"enquete-exemplo\",\n    \"title\": \"Qual sua linguagem favorita?\",\n    \"total_votes\": 42,\n    \"options\": [\n      { \"id\": 1, \"title\": \"PHP\", \"votes\": 20, \"percentage\": 47.6 },\n      { \"id\": 2, \"title\": \"Python\", \"votes\": 15, \"percentage\": 35.7 },\n      { \"id\": 3, \"title\": \"JavaScript\", \"votes\": 7, \"percentage\": 16.7 }\n    ]\n  }\n}",
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json"
        },
        {
          "name": "403 Forbidden — resultados não públicos",
          "status": "Forbidden",
          "code": 403,
          "header": [
            { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
          ],
          "body": "{\n  \"error\": \"Os resultados desta enquete não estão disponíveis.\"\n}",
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json"
        },
        {
          "name": "404 Not Found — enquete inexistente",
          "status": "Not Found",
          "code": 404,
          "header": [
            { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
          ],
          "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Not Found\"\n}",
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
